metric_cfgs.description: Total area of always on instances

metric_cfgs.scan_tcl: set_alert_metric -id $db_id -uuid $self_uuid -name $metric "Buffer area increased by over 20%" -condition [expr { [lindex $previous 0 0] ne {} && [lindex $self 0] ne {} && ( [lindex $previous 0 0] == 0 || (([lindex $self 0] * 100) / [lindex $previous 0 0]) >= 120) }]
